Biography
Dharmesh Shah, Agile Coach
Seeing many companies struggling with the implementation of the Agile methodology, decided to move to Training and Coaching to help teams adopt Lean and Agile principles and reap the benefit. As I see, the problem is not the lack of Will on part of the company, but while implementing only few processes and the focus on the Principles is lost. This is due to the lack of in-depth knowledge of Lean and Agile along with poor training.
